# Build-specific ignore for apps/site/Dockerfile (BuildKit uses
# <dockerfile>.dockerignore in preference to the repo-root .dockerignore).
#
# The root .dockerignore excludes `apps/site`, `**/docs`, `**/reference`, and
# `**/README.md` (the site was historically NOT containerized). This build IS the
# site, so it must INCLUDE apps/site and its docs pages — we only strip build
# artifacts + node_modules so the workspace install/build is clean and the
# context stays small.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/out
**/build
.git
.github
**/.github
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/coverage
**/package-lock.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/npm-debug.log*
**/.DS_Store
apps/forge-desktop
